						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of Mallam Koṇḍēśvarasvāmi temple on the hill.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Sarvadhāri chaitra śu. 10,</hi> may be in characters of 17th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>It records the construction of a temple by Rāmireḍi, son of Koṇḍāreḍi of Ōbaḷam and also mentions the construction of steps leading up to hill by Vuppuṭūri Pōtireḍḍi and Yallayya.</p>						

						</summary>
